  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dc3\u0d9a \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0db4\u0dd3 \u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The car crashed into a tree and a young man was killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Bibila police say that a nineteen-year-old young man died and his father was seriously injured and admitted to Badulla General Hospital yesterday evening at about 6.45 pm when a car ran off the road and hit a tree in Puwakpale area of \u200b\u200bBibila road.",
        "E.H.M., who was residing in Padiyathalawa High Street, died in the accident. A nineteen-year-old named Salinda Sitmina studied at Bibila Wellassa College.",
        "A religious preacher who conducts external graduate support classes has been seriously injured in the accident.",
        "While these two were coming home from Bibili, a wild elephant jumped on the road in the Puakpale Reserve and once the vehicle could not be stopped and the vehicle ran off the road and crashed into a bamboo tree. As two wild elephants roamed nearby, the injured had to wait for the Bibila police to take them to the hospital.",
        "The seriously injured person was transferred to Bibila Hospital and then to Monaragala Sirigala Hospital and then to Badulla General Hospital for further treatment."
      ],
